### Nuxt 3 / Frontend
- Auto-imports for all Vue/Nuxt composables — no manual imports needed
- useAsyncData / useFetch for data fetching — never onMounted fetch for SSR
- Server routes in server/api/ using defineEventHandler
- definePageMeta() on every page (layout + middleware)
- useSeoMeta() or useHead() on every page for SEO
- NuxtLink for all internal navigation
- Pinia for global state management (auto-imported stores)
- CSS variables for theming — never hardcoded color values
